Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.70,0:06:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.37,0:06:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.45,0:06:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.93,0:06:39.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.06,0:06:39.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.60,0:06:40.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被看到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.34,0:06:49.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好会被看光的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.41,0:06:56.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞啊，别看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.69,0:07:12.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸了会有感觉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.85,0:07:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,害羞，但好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.21,0:08:03.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别一直看啊，拜托
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.45,0:08:41.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有看着吗?
